data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house offers immense potential and is a fantastic opportunity for those looking to personalize their dream home. Boasting a range of attractive features, including a new electrical box, new windows, new furnace and a new roof! The three bedrooms offer ample space and natural light, providing a peaceful retreat for everyone in the household. One of the highlights of this property is the fenced-in yard, offering privacy and security for your outdoor activities and enjoyment. Additionally, a barn and a detached 2-stall garage provide ample storage space and the potential for a workshop or hobby area. Embrace the challenge and take advantage of this home's excellent location and desirable features. Bring your vision and transform this house into your dream home, tailored to your exact specifications.
